OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FThousands of young Indians have taken
OL,7,Fto the streets in New Delhi as part of
OL,8,Fthe 'Cockroach' movement, a youth-led
OL,9,Fcampaign targeting exam leaks,
OL,10,Funemployment and government
OL,11,Faccountability.
OL,13,FThe movement, organised by the
OL,14,FCockroach Janta Party (CJP), has
OL,15,Fbecome one of the most unexpected
OL,16,Fchallenges to Prime Minister Narendra
OL,17,FModi's government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
