OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FWhat began as an online satire
OL,7,Fcampaign has grown into a major street
OL,8,Fprotest movement, driven by anger over
OL,9,Falleged failures in India's
OL,10,Fexamination system and wider
OL,11,Ffrustrations among young people.
OL,13,FProtesters and police clashed on
OL,14,FMonday, marking one of the most
OL,15,Fsignificant moments in the CJP's two-
OL,16,Fmonth campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
