PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FDespite the confrontation,
OL,7,Fdemonstrators vowed to continue their
OL,8,Fprotest on Tuesday, refusing to leave
OL,9,Ftheir sit-in site in New Delhi after
OL,10,Fpolice used tear gas and batons to
OL,11,Fdisperse thousands attempting to march
OL,12,Ftowards parliament.
OL,14,FHundreds of protesters remained camped
OL,15,Fat Jantar Mantar under heavy police
OL,16,Fpresence, demanding the resignation of
OL,17,FEducation Minister Dharmendra Pradhan
OL,18,Fover alleged failures in India's
OL,19,Fexamination system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
