OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FBut who are the 'Cockroach' movement,
OL,7,Fhow were they formed, and what are
OL,8,Ftheir aims and objectives?
OL,10,FWhat is the 'Cockroach' movement?
OL,12,FThe Cockroach movement began as a
OL,13,Fsatirical online project but has
OL,14,Fquickly become a platform for millions
OL,15,Fof young Indians expressing
OL,16,Ffrustration over unemployment, rising
OL,17,Fliving costs, exam leaks and
OL,18,Fgovernment accountability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
