PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FAt its centre is the Cockroach Janta
OL,7,FParty - a parody political party that
OL,8,Fuses the cockroach as its symbol.
OL,10,FThrough memes, short videos and online
OL,11,Fsatire, the group has turned humour
OL,12,Finto a form of political protest.
OL,14,FThe cockroach was chosen because of
OL,15,Fits reputation for surviving harsh
OL,16,Fconditions, becoming a tongue-in-cheek
OL,17,Fsymbol of resilience among young
OL,18,Fpeople who feel ignored by those in
OL,19,Fpower.
OL,21,FHow did it start?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
