OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FThe CJP emerged online after comments
OL,7,Fby Supreme Court Chief Justice Surya
OL,8,FKant triggered backlash among young
OL,9,FIndians already frustrated by
OL,10,Funemployment, rising living costs and
OL,11,Falleged exam paper leaks affecting
OL,12,Frecruitment.
OL,14,FDuring a hearing in May, Kant
OL,15,Fcriticised what he described as
OL,16,F"parasites" targeting institutions and
OL,17,Fcompared some unemployed young people
OL,18,Fand activists to cockroaches.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,F"There are youngsters like
OL,7,Fcockroaches, who don't get any
OL,8,Femployment or have any place in the
OL,9,Fprofession," Kant said, adding that
OL,10,Fsome had turned to social media
OL,11,Factivism, journalism and public
OL,12,Finterest campaigns before "attacking
OL,13,Feveryone".
OL,15,FThe comments spread quickly online,
OL,16,Fwith many users accusing the judge of
OL,17,Fignoring the struggles of young
OL,18,FIndians.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]tD@[OUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FKant later clarified that he was
OL,7,Freferring to people getting fraudulent
OL,8,Fdegrees and said he did not intend to
OL,9,Finsult India's youth.
OL,11,FHowever, the controversy helped spark
OL,12,Fthe creation of the parody Cockroach
OL,13,FJanta Party account on Instagram,
OL,14,Fwhich adopted the insect as its
OL,15,Fpolitical symbol and began sharing
OL,16,Fmemes, mock campaign slogans and
OL,17,Fsatirical criticism of Modi's
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
