OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FWithin days, the movement attracted
OL,7,Ftens of thousands of online volunteers
OL,8,Fthrough a Google form, while some
OL,9,Fopposition figures also expressed
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,F"We have to understand that five years
OL,13,Fago nobody was ready to speak up
OL,14,Fagainst Modi or the government. The
OL,15,Ftimes are changing," Abhijeet Dipke,
OL,16,Ffounder of the CJP, said.
OL,18,FHow does the movement use satire?
OL,20,FThe Cockroach Janta Party leans
OL,21,Fheavily into self-mockery.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
