PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FIts tongue-in-cheek membership
OL,7,Fcriteria include being unemployed,
OL,8,Flazy, chronically online and capable
OL,9,Fof "ranting professionally".
OL,11,FIts mock manifesto uses satire to
OL,12,Fhighlight a range of contentious
OL,13,Fissues in Indian politics, including
OL,14,Fopposition allegations of voter
OL,15,Fmanipulation, criticism of the
OL,16,Frelationship between corporate media
OL,17,Fand the government, and the
OL,18,Fappointment of retired judges to
OL,19,Fofficial posts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
