SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FCritics, many of them supporters of
OL,7,FModi, have dismissed the movement as
OL,8,Fan online political gimmick aligned
OL,9,Fwith the opposition, pointing to
OL,10,Ffounder Dipke's previous links to the
OL,11,FAam Aadmi Party.
OL,13,FThey also argue the movement's
OL,14,Fpopularity is unlikely to last,
OL,15,Fclaiming it is a social media campaign
OL,16,Frather than a genuine grassroots
OL,17,Fmovement.
OL,19,FBut Dipke insists the campaign has
OL,20,Fgrown beyond the internet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
