PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,F"This is the movement that has arrived
OL,7,Fin India ... it will change the
OL,8,Fpolitical discourse," he said. "It
OL,9,Fwill continue online, and if required
OL,10,Fit will also come on the ground."
OL,12,FHow is the state responding?
OL,14,FThe government's response has come
OL,15,Funder increasing scrutiny following
OL,16,Fclashes between protesters and police
OL,17,Fin New Delhi on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
