OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FSocial media videos show officers
OL,7,Fhitting demonstrators with batons and
OL,8,Fdragging protesters away, spreading
OL,9,Frapidly across social media, fuelling
OL,10,Fpublic anger.
OL,12,FSome footage showed young protesters
OL,13,Fcrying and pleading with police to
OL,14,Fstop hitting them, while other clips
OL,15,Fcaptured demonstrators standing their
OL,16,Fground despite repeated baton strikes.
OL,18,FDelhi Police said nearly 180 people
OL,19,Fwere injured in the confrontation,
OL,20,Fincluding 118 security personnel and
OL,21,F60 protesters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
