PN,31614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FAmong those at the demonstration was
OL,7,F20-year-old student Sona Bisht, who
OL,8,Fsaid the police action had only
OL,9,Fstrengthened her determination.
OL,11,F"If the government thinks that doing
OL,12,Fthis with Gen Z, they can stop us,
OL,13,Fthen that won't happen," she said.
OL,15,F"We are here talking about education,
OL,16,Ftalking about securing our future. And
OL,17,Ftill the time our demands are not met,
OL,18,Fwe will not move from here."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
