PN,31615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,FAfter almost a month of silence, the
OL,7,Fgovernment made its first apparent
OL,8,Fattempt to engage with the movement on
OL,9,FMonday, when a senior minister met
OL,10,Frepresentatives from the CJP.
OL,12,FHowever, the talks failed to calm
OL,13,Ftensions, with protest leaders saying
OL,14,Fthey wanted concrete action rather
OL,15,Fthan assurances.
OL,17,FAmnesty International condemned the
OL,18,Fpolice response, saying it
OL,19,Fdemonstrated "how peaceful dissent is
OL,20,Fbeing suppressed in India".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
