OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784679493
OL,3,CWhat is India's Cockroach movement?
OL,4,CThe youth-led protest challenging Modi
OL,6,F"The role of the authorities is to
OL,7,Fprotect and facilitate peaceful
OL,8,Fprotests, not to suppress them," the
OL,9,Forganisation said.
OL,11,F"The right to freedom of peaceful
OL,12,Fassembly is recognised under
OL,13,Finternational human rights law and the
OL,14,FIndian Constitution."
